      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a flawless Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically optimized with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement already completed. The chassis remains remarkably rigid, supported by precision-tuned suspension and staggered forged alloys. With consistent paint depth across all panels and an interior that retains its factory-fresh tactile feel, this is a turn-key masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
